 ["serial and government publications division"], "partof_title": ["norwich bulletin (norwich, conn.) 1895-2011"], "place_of_publication": "Norwich, Conn.", "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "raw_lccn": "sn 82014086 ", "reel_numbers": ["00295866330"], "resources": [{"files": 14, "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ct:batch_ct_canaan_ver01:data:sn82014086:00295866330:1921010801:0085/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn82014086/1921-01-08/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "rights": ["<p>The Library of Congress believes that the newspapers in Chronicling America are in the public domain or have no known copyright restrictions.  Newspapers published in the United States more than 95 years ago are in the public domain in their entirety. Any newspapers in Chronicling America that were published less than 95 years ago are also believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.332207, "shard": "07", "shelf_id": "sn82014086, 1921-01-08, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/ct", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["new london", "newspapers", "new london county (conn.)", "windham county (conn.)", "norwich", "connecticut", "new london county", "windham county", "united states", "norwich (conn.)"], "subject_headings": ["Norwich (Conn.)--Newspapers", "New London County (Conn.)--Newspapers", "Windham County (Conn.)--Newspapers", "Connecticut--New London County", "Connecticut--Norwich", "Connecticut--Windham County", "United States--Connecticut--New London--Norwich"], "subjects": [{"connecticut": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:connecticut&fo=json"}, {"new london": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:new+london&fo=json"}, {"new london county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:new+london+county&fo=json"}, {"new london county (conn.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:new+london+county+%28conn.%29&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"norwich": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:norwich&fo=json"}, {"norwich (conn.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:norwich+%28conn.%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}, {"windham county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:windham+county&fo=json"}, {"windham county (conn.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:windham+county+%28conn.%29&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2023-06-28T06:54:04.367Z", "title": "Norwich bulletin (Norwich, Conn.), January 8, 1921", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn82014086/1921-01-08/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://lccn.loc.gov/sn82014086", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn82014086/", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/97bd99f0-b24b-5adf-ba3d-cf2647789f41"], "batch": ["ct_andover_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1895", "description": ["Daily, Nov. 2, 1930- Began in 1895; ceased with Feb. 28, 2011. \"Republican.\" On Sundays published as: Norwich Sunday record, <July 1, 1934>-May 12, 1957, and: Norwich bulletin-record, May 19-26, 1957, and: Norwich bulletin record, June 1957-Mar. 15, 1981, and Sunday bulletin, Mar. 22, 1981- Includes section with separate designation called: The Courier, <Mar. 1, 1964>-Mar. 2, 1980. Published in regional editions for New London County and Windham County: June 19, 1990- Includes weekly sections called: Windhan County transcript, and: Community transcript, and: Shoreline transcript, Jan. 14, 1998- Articles selectively issued in CD-ROM version as part of: Newsbank News File, and as part of Newsbank Reference Services. Issues for Nov. 22, 1937-May 19, 1975 lack numbering. Available on microfilm from UMI and from Connecticut State Library, Hartford, Conn. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Evening ed.: Norwich evening record, Nov. 1927-June 27, 1952. Semiweekly ed.: Norwich courier (Norwich, Conn. : 1901), <Mar. 12, 1901>-Oct. 1927. Weekly eds.: Norwich weekly courier (Norwich, Conn. : 1860), <1895>, and: Norwich bulletin, Norwich courier, Cooley's weekly, Nov. 5, 1927, and: Norwich courier-Cooley's weekly, Nov. 11, 1927-Oct. 1930. Description based on: Vol. 37, no. 192 (Aug. 12, 1895). Latest issue consulted: Feb. 28, 2011. Bulletin (Norwich, Conn.) (DLC) 2014218246 (OCoLC)707099581"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:01.070Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "catalog-split-14", "catalog", "ndnp/newspapers", "main-catalog-split-14", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn82014086/", "image_url": [], "index": 12, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [41.524304, -72.075821], "location": ["new london", "norwich", "connecticut", "new london county", "windham county", "u