-26, 1957, and: Norwich bulletin record, June 1957-Mar. 15, 1981, and Sunday bulletin, Mar. 22, 1981- Includes section with separate designation called: The Courier, <Mar. 1, 1964>-Mar. 2, 1980. Published in regional editions for New London County and Windham County: June 19, 1990- Includes weekly sections called: Windham County transcript, and: Community transcript, and: Shoreline transcript, Jan. 14, 1998- Articles selectively issued on CD-ROM version as part of: Newsbank News File, and as part of Newsbank Reference Services. Issues for Nov. 22, 1937-May 19, 1975 lack numbering. Available on microfilm from UMI and from Connecticut State Library, Hartford, Conn. Evening ed.: Norwich evening record, Nov. 1927-June 27, 1952. Semiweekly ed.: Norwich courier (Norwich, Conn. : 1901), <Mar. 12, 1901>-Oct. 1927. Weekly eds.: Norwich weekly courier (Norwich, Conn. : 1860), <1895>, and: Norwich bulletin, Norwich courier, Cooley's weekly, Nov. 5, 1927, and: Norwich courier-Cooley's weekly, Nov. 11, 1927-Oct. 1930. Description based on: Vol. LII, no. 1 (January 1, 1910); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed February 26, 2015). Latest issue consulted: Vol. LXIV, no. 312 December 30, 1922) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed February 26, 2015). Bulletin (Norwich, Conn.)"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:36:39.438Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2015218553/", "image_url": [], "index": 13, "language": ["english"], "location": ["new london", "norwich", "connecticut", "new london county", "windham county", "united states"], "number": ["sn92051435", "online resource", "2377-5874", "2015218553", "sn82015887", "50907842", "sn92051444", "sn92051448", "sn84022587", "sn92051443", "sn92051341", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Norwich Sunday record", "Norwich bulletin-record", "Sunday bulletin", "Morning bulletin, w